The paper proposes a formal definition for the quality of a given dataset and utilizes mathematical methods to assess it. It also focuses on Boolean hyperplanes and utilizes Fourier analytic, algebraic, and probabilistic methods. These characteristics suggest that the paper is most likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category, as well as the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Theory (cs.IT), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories.
